<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      I know Hendra's market well. The buyers here are typically families and professionals who have been searching in Ascot and Hamilton, encountered the premium pricing of those suburbs, and arrived in Hendra as a deliberate and well-researched alternative. They are not settling. They are making an informed decision that Hendra offers comparable streetscape quality, comparable school access and comparable CBD proximity at a price point that reflects genuine value rather than scarcity.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The best Hendra properties are well-maintained or well-renovated Queenslanders and character Federation homes on 600 square metre or larger blocks. These attract a genuinely competitive buyer pool at auction. The Eagle Farm and Doomben racing precinct brings its own distinct buyer segment: buyers connected to the racing industry who want proximity to the course without Ascot's price expectations. This adds a second buyer pool that operates somewhat independently of the broader prestige market and can produce strong results for the right properties.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Inner-North Prestige Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Hendra, Ascot, Clayfield corridor</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #b98229;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#191817; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Character Heritage Market</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Strong Ascot-Hamilton overflow demand</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/ascot" style="color:#b98229;">Ascot</a>, <a href="/suburbs/clayfield" style="color:#b98229;">Clayfield</a>, <a href="/suburbs/hamilton" style="color:#b98229;">Hamilton</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

